{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idbf7945d2-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12573"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"12573"},"text":"§ 12573.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Types of national service positions eligible for approval for national service educational awards","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The Corporation may approve of any of the following service positions as an approved national service position that includes the national service educational award described in division D as one of the benefits to be provided for successful service in the position:","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbf7945d3-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12573/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" A position for a participant in a national service program described in subsection (a), (b), or (c) of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s12572"},"text":"section 12572 of this title","children":[],"tail":" that receives assistance under subsection (a) of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s12571"},"text":"section 12571 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbf7945d4-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12573/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" A position for a participant in a program that—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idbf7945d5-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12573/2/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" is carried out by a State, a subdivision of a State, a territory, an Indian tribe, a public or private nonprofit organization, an institution of higher education, or a Federal agency (under an interagency agreement described in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s12571/b"},"text":"section 12571(b) of this title","children":[],"tail":"); and"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idbf7945d6-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12573/2/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" would be eligible to receive assistance under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s12571/a"},"text":"section 12571(a) of this title","children":[],"tail":", based on criteria established by the Corporation, but has not applied for such assistance."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbf7945d7-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12573/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" A position involving service as a VISTA volunteer under title I of the Domestic Volunteer Service Act of 1973 (","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s4951"},"text":"42 U.S.C. 4951","children":[],"tail":" et seq.)."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbf7945d8-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12573/4"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4"},"text":"(4)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" A position facilitating service-learning in a program described in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s12572/a/1/B/vi"},"text":"section 12572(a)(1)(B)(vi) of this title","children":[],"tail":" that is eligible for assistance under part I of division B."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbf7945d9-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12573/5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"5"},"text":"(5)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" A position for a participant in the National Civilian Community Corps under division E.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbf7945da-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12573/6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"6"},"text":"(6)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" A position involving service as a crew leader in a youth corps program or a similar position supporting a national service program that receives an approved national service position.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbf7945db-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12573/7"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"7"},"text":"(7)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" A position involving service in the ServeAmerica Fellowship program carried out under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s12653b"},"text":"section 12653b of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbf7945dc-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12573/8"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"8"},"text":"(8)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Such other national service positions as the Corporation considers to be appropriate.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idbf7945dd-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/610/tI/s123"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–610, title I, § 123","children":[],"tail":", as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/82/tI/s101/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–82, title I, § 101(b)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1993-09-21"},"text":"Sept. 21, 1993","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/107/794"},"text":"107 Stat. 794","children":[],"tail":"; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/13/tI/s1303"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–13, title I, § 1303","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2009-04-21"},"text":"Apr. 21, 2009","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/123/1499"},"text":"123 Stat. 1499","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idbf7945de-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idbf7945df-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idbf7945e0-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Domestic Volunteer Service Act of 1973, referred to in par. (3), is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/93/113"},"text":"Pub. L. 93–113","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1973-10-01"},"text":"Oct. 1, 1973","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/87/394"},"text":"87 Stat. 394","children":[],"tail":". Title I of the Act is classified generally to subchapter I (§ 4951 et seq.) of chapter 66 of this title. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s4950"},"text":"section 4950 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"t